reviewText: Super fast shipping and great quality! The workout is amazing! Even though they are a few years old the  pilates moves do not change.

This video did an okay job of getting the heart-rate up, but not exactly what I was looking for.  I wanted something a little more "cardio" but I guess there's only so much cardio you can do with the malibu pilates machine.
Easy to do and does gets your heart pumping. Loving it even more, because I found the pilates chair at a 2nd hand store for cheap! Win/Win.
